    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true 'time capsule' vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, and its condition is absolute. The exterior paint boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the factory alloy wheels are flawless, with no curb rash or pitting. Step inside to an interior that still retains its new-car aroma; the premium leather seats are supple and matte, showing no signs of wear, creasing, or sun fading. All dashboard surfaces, wood veneers, and tactile buttons are in pristine condition, with every electronic system and sensor functioning with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified specialists. The engine bay is detailed to show-quality standards, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a thick folder of maintenance documentation. This is an investment-grade example for a collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
