      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, and it\u2019s been kept tucked away in a garage. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
